nhc_headline: ...PRISCILLA LIKELY TO STRENGTHEN OVER THE NEXT COUPLE OF DAYS...
summary: ...PRISCILLA LIKELY TO STRENGTHEN OVER THE NEXT COUPLE OF DAYS... As of 11:00 PM MST Sat Oct 04 the center of Priscilla was located near 15.8, -106.8 with movement NW at 3 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1000 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
